text: It is a wonderful neighbourhood church. A hidden gem that should be known by more people. The children service is fun. The fellowship is warm. The sermon is biblical and relevant.
1 of the few earlier church that still standing on original site. Good old fashioned type of worship with some technology upgrade. Worth visiting if you are interested in old school stuffs.
